    <content type="html">        &lt;body&gt;
            &lt;img src="https://image-cdn.tver.jp/images/content/thumbnail/series/xlarge/sr2qsz7e4k.jpg"&gt;

            &lt;hr&gt;

            &lt;div&gt;🎞️ LOVED ONE
